<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Emotions in Music Genres | Contents</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f7f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        /* Grid for the 4 emotion types */
        .emotion-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .emotion-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 5px solid #2c3e50;
        }
        .emotion-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .img-placeholder {
            background: #e1e8ed;
            height: 120px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #777;
        }
        .stats {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: left;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-back { background: #95a5a6; color: white; }
        .btn-next { background: #2c3e50; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Emotions in Music Genres</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <p>Explore how different emotions are expressed through specific musical elements like tempo and key.</p>

        <div class="emotion-grid">
            <div class="emotion-card">
               <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/ad/ca/e3/adcae35e1de1e763ecfa8f8feb9160ce.jpg" alt="Happiness description" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px;">
                <h3>Happiness</h3>
                <div class="stats">
                    • <strong>Tempo:</strong> Fast<br>
                    • <strong>Key:</strong> Major keys
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="emotion-card">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/9c/ac/ae/9cacaeb501a3789eb2eef7f8461c96bb.jpg" alt="Happiness description" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px;">
                <h3>Sadness</h3>
                <div class="stats">
                    • <strong>Tempo:</strong> Slow<br>
                    • <strong>Key:</strong> Minor keys
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="emotion-card">
               <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/99/fb/e6/99fbe63533c143c0347fdc177bf5061a.jpg" alt="Happiness description" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px;">
                <h3>Anger</h3>
                <div class="stats">
                    • <strong>Sound:</strong> Loud<br>
                    • <strong>Rhythm:</strong> Strong
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="emotion-card">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/6d/de/c9/6ddec9ebeccb3fd1b9ac6a5f1251cb23.jpg" alt="Happiness description" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px;">
                <h3>Calm</h3>
                <div class="stats">
                    • <strong>Melody:</strong> Soft<br>
                    • <strong>Rhythm:</strong> Slow
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

